  <description>
    <p>**Super Linux Utility** is a full-featured application for managing and optimizing your Linux system.</p>
    <p>Main features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Analyse and manage systemd services (identify services that slow down boot)</li>
      <li>Manage startup applications with protection for system apps</li>
      <li>Clean temporary files from common applications</li>
      <li>Manage installed apps (APT, Snap, Flatpak, GNOME) with dependency checks</li>
      <li>Monitor processes and system resources (CPU, RAM, disks, GPU)</li>
      <li>Disk usage analyzer</li>
      <li>Customize appearance (font, themes, icons, wallpaper)</li>
      <li>Advanced mode (optional): GRUB editor with automatic backup, kernel management, system recovery</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Available in two editions: standard (free) and advanced (paid, with GRUB, Kernel and Recovery tools).</p>
  </description>

